Ian Wright has hailed Chelsea 's up-and-coming star Jay Dasilva , claiming he is better than any current left back in the Barclays Premier League .
The 16-year-old was part of the Chelsea Under 19 team won the UEFA Youth League by beating Shakhtar Donetsk in Monday 's final in Nyon , Switzerland .
Chelsea became the first English team to win the Youth League after 3-2 win .